name: Prime Day
summary: Amazon Prime Day, an annual shopping event, is approaching with significant savings. Various outlets report early access to deals on products such as car accessories, tech, TVs, and more. ZDNet provides information on Prime Day 2024, including upcoming dates and deals available now. Engadget highlights the best tech deals ahead of the sale. NBC News announces the dates for this year's Prime Day: July 16 and 17. About Amazon previews deals from brands like New Balance and Sony. Vox.com discusses the expansion of Prime Day beyond Amazon. CNN Underscored urges shoppers to take advantage of early deals as they become available. ABC News questions the value of Prime Day deals. Finally, Yahoo Life offers a list of 40+ Prime Day deals with up to 70% savings.
